	! !!StickyPadMorph commentStamp: 'sw 3/3/2004 13:31' prior: 0!A custom item for the  Squeakland Supplies bin, as defined by Kim Rose and BJ Con.A parts bin will deliver up translucent, borderless Rectangles in a sequence of 6 colors.  It offers some complication to the parts-bin protocols in two ways::
